Class projectTwo.Run_Bank

java.lang.Object
projectTwo.Run_Bank
public class projectTwo.Run_Bank extends Object
This is our teams driver class, which allows us to create and manipulate the objects we have designed for the project. This class also allows us to read and create Excel file (.xlsx) as well as log any interaction of the user with the system.
